<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad d. J. von Rosenberg, Amtmann zu Reichelsburg</head><p>Der Rat teilt Unkenntnis wegen einer Anfrage nach Geleit zur Frankfurter Fastenmesse mit; es ist ohnehin ungewiss, ob Nürnberger Kaufleute die Messe besuchen werden.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_403" id="201r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_403_r1l28"><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Roſenperg <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Jungen cʒü </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r1l29">Poxperg / Amptman cʒü <expan>Reygelb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_403_r1l30"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / wie ew <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> knechte geſagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r1l31"><expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mit Jn geredt hab / von geleittes <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> in die nehſtkomenden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r1l32"><expan>frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vaſte<ex>n</ex>meʒʒ</expan> / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / . vnd <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r1l33"><expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wiſſen / . daʒ wir <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ſölıcher rede nicht wiſſen / vnd wıſſen auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r1l34">noch nicht / ob die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / die meſſe ſüchen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht / Dann wir <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r1l35">wo dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> geleittes <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒü ew <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ſie ew beuolhen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r1l36">laſſet ſein / Als wir ew ſünderlıch vvol getrawen vnd vmb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r1l37">allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ̃ . <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Paulı <expan>Co<ex>n</ex>u<ex>er</ex>ſ<ex>ionem</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_403" id="201r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Rosenperg <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> jungen czü
                        Poxperg, amptman czü <expan>Reygelb<ex>er</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ew
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> knechte gesagt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> der
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mit in geredt hab von geleittes
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> in die nehstkomenden
                                <expan>Frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vaste<ex>n</ex>mezz</expan>, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
                        wissen, daz wir <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> sölicher rede nicht wissen; und
                        wissen auch noch nicht, ob die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> die messe
                        süchen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht. Dann wir
                        <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, wo die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> geleittes <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> czü ew
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz ir sie ew bevolhen lasset sein,
                        als wir ew sünderlich wol getrawen und umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> allczeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Pauli
                                <expan>co<ex>n</ex>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>ionem</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
